Subject: Re: 2.4.9-ac17 Adaptec AIC7XXX problems (new driver, old one works fine) (solved)
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
